3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of deep generative neural networks for facial expression synthesis. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a potential category as the paper deals with image and video manipulation. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper involves generating realistic facial expressions in still images.
